{"tid":476002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做完植髮一年,你問我答","createTime":"2017-11-21T15:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T16:24:08.000Z","uid":142475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2961372ed202788cfcaf04404acdfc7585c8ccba","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061eecd425c313bf9290c8c0646135e58537f769","tid":476002,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"幾錢 <br />\n做個陣痛唔痛 <br />\n會唔會唔自然 <br />\n本身甩到點<br />\n有冇壽命?"},{"pid":"4a88254f35de636e98b8361737cd8dbcebb98e03","tid":476002,"uid":138252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"有冇對比圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4458c228c0d00d8d1a9ab68637525f2a8da629","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:24:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢 <br />\n做個陣痛唔痛 <br />\n會唔會唔自然 <br />\n本身甩到點<br />\n有冇壽命?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n20000蚊<br />\n取髮既時候都痛,尤其麻醉藥開始過既時候<br />\n做到好自然,壽命同我一樣咁耐"},{"pid":"f7d1c92649044ced4be6980ef39f4849d704eacd","tid":476002,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾錢 <br />\n做個陣痛唔痛 <br />\n會唔會唔自然 <br />\n本身甩到點<br />\n有冇壽命?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n20000蚊<br />\n取髮既時候都痛,尤其麻醉藥開始過既時候<br />\n做到好自然,壽命同我一樣咁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我想填左兩邊m 大概要幾錢?"},{"pid":"63837964ade610473085d4064ece92e02a863183","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇對比圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n初時好on9冇影到,總之之前成個比達咁。而家就咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/232810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F232810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9cdb09f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8df663699fb75378458e3c75761c2ebdd2434d49","tid":476002,"uid":71524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾錢 <br />\n做個陣痛唔痛 <br />\n會唔會唔自然 <br />\n本身甩到點<br />\n有冇壽命?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n20000蚊<br />\n取髮既時候都痛,尤其麻醉藥開始過既時候<br />\n做到好自然,壽命同我一樣咁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<br />\n我想整返個頭頂呀<br />\n係唔係一樣價錢？"},{"pid":"b358f261d0caca52a48bf2f3340b089945a07de6","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾錢 <br />\n做個陣痛唔痛 <br />\n會唔會唔自然 <br />\n本身甩到點<br />\n有冇壽命?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n20000蚊<br />\n取髮既時候都痛,尤其麻醉藥開始過既時候<br />\n做到好自然,壽命同我一樣咁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我想填左兩邊m 大概要幾錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我番左大陸做,好平.睇你睇唔睇膽。香港做係會貴3到5倍左右"},{"pid":"c500961ef57966d15fd4e4f06380b597e073da30","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾錢 <br />\n做個陣痛唔痛 <br />\n會唔會唔自然 <br />\n本身甩到點<br />\n有冇壽命?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n20000蚊<br />\n取髮既時候都痛,尤其麻醉藥開始過既時候<br />\n做到好自然,壽命同我一樣咁耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<br />\n我想整返個頭頂呀<br />\n係唔係一樣價錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n度度一樣價錢,不過頭頂查野都可以救得番,唔一定要植髮"},{"pid":"522627dc97097c047b8bdceff8d8575b4cdcd0b2","tid":476002,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"要幾多日先出得街？"},{"pid":"f3d07a973efc0e05aaa32302a8767321d5d1376a","tid":476002,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df39c4a2a3b9bfa074d8619fe447d97d512f5b29","tid":476002,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"267b70418976c9dcdf6c4f4f6457b79a179af550","tid":476002,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d26fb5ee4873e9005a4ed616b7d856da46117d4","tid":476002,"uid":159333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"後面疤痕位有無生到頭髮？"},{"pid":"9cdc025e5eb521f6272ecb409f27a66bfd375cf9","tid":476002,"uid":50,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"25歲仔我都M額現型<br />\n係唔係越早做越好"},{"pid":"3f4cdcf7a3ae977c03415b4b6e544a920588794c","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要幾多日先出得街？</blockquote><br />\n我做FUE, 4日就出得了"},{"pid":"9f17f57ec22e66be920e136efd84c3d695c27963","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要唔要食一世保絲康？</blockquote><br />\n唔會食,隻野副作用好勁。我寧願辛苦d用5%"},{"pid":"9783b8ce96b7d16b7b5433dd851f5cc8e5b28239","tid":476002,"uid":52355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"純植M字有咩要注意"},{"pid":"cd067215d0ae2e1f0110ead7c8108ed47626606f","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>稙完過幾耐自無血痕？<br />\n中間時間你點姐醜？長期帶帽？<br />\n返工同事點講？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做完4日後醫院就會同你洗d血,所以連埋星期六日,我請左3日大假<br />\n而由於我冇剃光,所以d同事只係以後我換左新髮形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8d8f42a65a4b18d60111d9c4ade08168d91d0e","tid":476002,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:57:38.000Z","msg":"如果天生髮線高想植低d得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d98698a6d79224bfbd2b2879fb43db44a40a185","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被拔走既地方而定點？<br />\n剪頭髮有無野要注意？<br />\n<br />\n利申， 有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拔走左之後個毛囊位唔會生番頭髮,所以頭髮比平時疏,但一般唔講d人唔覺。<br />\n10日後剪頭髮冇問題,因為是真髮。"},{"pid":"314d6957c3aa99c79018a6ad320ab18fe21a92cc","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後面疤痕位有無生到頭髮？</blockquote><br />\nFeu一條條咁抽,所以冇疤痕"},{"pid":"9cae27609c8c45bc0d4bba5cc0ed6a4406818377","tid":476002,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:00:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇對比圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n初時好on9冇影到,總之之前成個比達咁。而家就咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/232810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F232810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9cdb09f6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前好誇張? 依家都好似唔係咁夠<br />\n唔知係咪關額高事<br />\n聽講毛囊一無就植唔到頭髮 真定假"},{"pid":"70b4b4afa9366762830ad464f18ed5aa8a9f6620","tid":476002,"uid":766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"咩原理？"},{"pid":"557995fb52aa45874062352d1451b7af060ed53e","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>25歲仔我都M額現型<br />\n係唔係越早做越好</blockquote><br />\n建議你用左護髮產品先,搞唔掂先考慮植。<br />\n不過m字位一般比較難生,植髮係最快既方法。"},{"pid":"7b9a53084559ffd027b63764926d53615b0b8e71","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純植M字有咩要注意</blockquote><br />\n你做完都要好好愛護d頭髮,用護髮產品。因為髮線是會越甩越上,如果植左前面又甩番中間就會變成河童頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a14c3cc7de80d418dc3080ee0789f1a97fd3f2","tid":476002,"uid":54909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"雄禿做 得唔得，會唔會貴d？"},{"pid":"77cce1c453aea26b2eeea192ac8e5e7ba2794a43","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果天生髮線高想植低d得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得,不過一生人可以植既數量有限,要小心使用"},{"pid":"fe36b381a057ac229c1bc3db9a388ec0be178af2","tid":476002,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果天生髮線高想植低d得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得,不過一生人可以植既數量有限,要小心使用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係髮線高巴打 <br />\n做左 就可以玩all back 了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaf58889c91d318634d599b508423beb047f7b4","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇對比圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n初時好on9冇影到,總之之前成個比達咁。而家就咁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/232810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F232810_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9cdb09f6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前好誇張? 依家都好似唔係咁夠<br />\n唔知係咪關額高事<br />\n聽講毛囊一無就植唔到頭髮 真定假</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我天生額高,而家個感覺是回到我未m之前,所以而家效果我好滿意<br />\n毛囊一無就植唔到頭髮&lt;--植髮原理是從後枕的毛囊移去甩髮區。如果你後枕側邊用哂咪冇得植"},{"pid":"6c9a866007b3c4c1f18915b2275a51df8652a39d","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雄禿做 得唔得，會唔會貴d？</blockquote><br />\n得,不過建議用左護髮產品先"},{"pid":"5a30b4466389fe93dd1a8e1d1ce5d20a965bbfa7","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果天生髮線高想植低d得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得,不過一生人可以植既數量有限,要小心使用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係髮線高巴打 <br />\n做左 就可以玩all back 了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，會多左好多玩法"},{"pid":"76ec5f6e1881222ceba933c49b08d2d638a279c3","tid":476002,"uid":54909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:20:27.000Z","msg":"可否加密share你做果間地址？"},{"pid":"45ddde24f5760082411934271a13a1f12e502656","tid":476002,"uid":50,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>25歲仔我都M額現型<br />\n係唔係越早做越好</blockquote><br />\n建議你用左護髮產品先,搞唔掂先考慮植。<br />\n不過m字位一般比較難生,植髮係最快既方法。</blockquote><br />\n有呀，我用緊DR.D <br />\n已經停左甩"},{"pid":"3c44263a482c41ad406492509c1014b480a456ed","tid":476002,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>25歲仔我都M額現型<br />\n係唔係越早做越好</blockquote><br />\n建議你用左護髮產品先,搞唔掂先考慮植。<br />\n不過m字位一般比較難生,植髮係最快既方法。</blockquote><br />\n有呀，我用緊DR.D <br />\n已經停左甩</blockquote><br />\n咩鋪會多呢d野賣"},{"pid":"b404e1b56d04b52cf1e69df18f9e149d10d9cf3d","tid":476002,"uid":50,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>25歲仔我都M額現型<br />\n係唔係越早做越好</blockquote><br />\n建議你用左護髮產品先,搞唔掂先考慮植。<br />\n不過m字位一般比較難生,植髮係最快既方法。</blockquote><br />\n有呀，我用緊DR.D <br />\n已經停左甩</blockquote><br />\n咩鋪會多呢d野賣</blockquote><br />\n我都係追POST見人介紹<br />\n我用左4-5個月左右<br />\n中間有一個月停左，成日懶唔去買<br />\n跟住甩番多左，同埋D頭髮明顯幼左好多<br />\n即刻去買番<br />\n<br />\n萬寧2百尾<br />\n上網買平D,佢地有FB你自已搵下"},{"pid":"bc8264271d74fe72d6ab869a4de57bf4ae1fa1b9","tid":476002,"uid":142475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T23:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可否加密share你做果間地址？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063e68e4b15ab